sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as UI
    participant SR as support_routes.py
    participant EH as entry_handler.py
    participant RH as reasoning_handler.py
    participant G as graph
    participant SN as start_node
    participant CN as context_node
    participant IC as intent_class_node
    participant QR as question_readiness_node
    participant RO as routing
    participant RF as response_formatter

    User->>UI: vague question, no case_id
    UI->>SR: POST /entry/reasoning
    Note over SR: handle_reasoning_entry() L108
    Note over SR: validate intent==AI_REASONING L109
    SR->>SR: _dispatch_entry_handler() L82
    SR->>EH: handle_entry(envelope) L84
    Note over EH: intent == AI_REASONING L67
    EH->>RH: handle_ai_reasoning() L68
    Note over RH: case_id = None L50
    RH->>G: graph.invoke(initial_state) L66

    G->>SN: start_node(state) L6
    SN-->>G: escalated flags = False

    G->>CN: context_node(state) L23
    Note over CN: case_id is None -> skip blob
    CN-->>G: case_context=None

    G->>IC: intent_classification_node(state) L11
    Note over IC: case_loaded = False L18
    Note over IC: llm.with_structured_output(_RawClass)
    IC-->>G: intent=OPERATIONAL, confidence=0.4

    G->>QR: question_readiness_node(state) L18
    Note over QR: OPERATIONAL not in ALWAYS_READY L13
    Note over QR: case_loaded = False
    Note over QR: get_llm("intent", 0.0)
    Note over QR: llm.with_structured_output(QRResult)
    QR-->>G: question_ready=False, clarifying_question

    G->>RO: route_question_readiness() L15
    Note over RO: not question_ready -> NOT_READY L16
    RO-->>G: NOT_READY -> response_formatter
    Note over G: skips router_node + all domain nodes

    G->>RF: response_formatter_node(state) L9
    Note over RF: question_ready=False path
    RF-->>G: final_response{clarifying_question}

    G-->>RH: graph_result

    Note over RH: question_ready==False L77
    RH->>RH: build_clarifying_question_response() L80
    Note over RH: status="ok" L134
    Note over RH: suggestions=_CLARIFYING_SUGGESTIONS
    RH-->>SR: EntryResponseEnvelope status=ok

    SR-->>UI: EntryResponseEnvelope
    UI-->>User: clarifying question + suggestion chips
